title: Yeomen.ai - Elevate your game!
description:
Web3 games bring about possibilities for autonomous worlds that traditional games are not able to offer. Yeomen.ai makes the on-chain data available to the masses in simple dashboards. Yeomen.ai also offers on-chain extension of autonomous worlds to automate and transform game play. Command has an Intents based services layer to offer services on Autonomous Worlds that can expand to all Web3.

Yeomen.ai can work with MUD or Dojo powered onchain games and financial applications in future.
